description:
Earth Choice Wool & Delicates Top & Front Loader Eucalyptus Fresh is plant based formula, grey water & septic safe, Australian made & owned and cruelty free.


Specially formulated with Eucalyptus Oil for effective cleaning yet gentle on your clothes. It is enriched with vegetable glycerin to keep woollens and delicates soft and lustrous for longer.

Sourced from Nature: - Plant Based Formula. - Readily Biodegradable Surfactants (to AS4351).

Grey Water & Septic Safe: - Low Sodium.

Cruelty Free: - CCF Accredited/Vegan.

Recycled Bottle: - 100% Post Consumer Recycled Plastic reduces the use of non renewable resources along with a significant reduction in carbon emissions.

Australian Made & Owned.

Natural Clean.

NP. Contains no phosphorus.
name: Earth Choice Wool Wash 1L
